        private void showPopupMenu(android.view.View view,

        Create and show a PopupMenu when an item of recyclerView is long clicked. The menu allows the user to move, edit or delete a JobApplication.
        Parameters:
        view - the view that has been long clicked (should be an item of recyclerView
        pos - the position of the clicked item
